      "BikeSeriesName": "Vida E+",
      "BikeSeriesDescription": "More powerful than ever, the new Vida E+ combines effortless speed, intelligent tech, and superior comfort to redefine your ride.\r\nPower That Delivers The Vida E’s powerful 500W motor and impressive 700Wh battery provide 28mph pedal assist, making steep hills, city cruising and everyday adventures effortless. Its optional throttle is a game-changing upgrade that delivers instant 20mph acceleration at your fingertips, no pedaling required.\r\nIntelligence in Motion True power demands smart engineering. Our breakthrough SyncDrive technology reads real-time data from three precision sensors, instantly calibrating the perfect boost for every single pedal stroke. The result? A ride so intuitive, it’s in sync with you. \r\nComfort Redefined Every detail is designed for your comfort. The low step-through frame suits riders of all abilities, while its 80mm travel suspension fork absorbs the road ahead for a super-smooth ride. A plush saddle and wide, grippy tires complete the ultimate comfort package for any terrain.  \r\nThere are no compromises with the Vida E: serious power, smart technology and all-day comfort put the fun and freedom back into riding, wherever you’re going. Enjoy La Vida today!",
      "Headline": "Fuel Your Freedom",
